Introduction

Kang Chanhee, popularly known as Chani, is a South Korean singer, rapper, and actor under FNC Entertainment. He made his official debut on October 5, 2016 as the maknae and rapper of the boy group SF9.

Before debuting, Chani was a child actor who starred in the MBC drama "Queen Seondeok". He continued acting after debuting as an idol and starred in dramas such as "Sky Castle", "Signal", and "Miracle".
